text: Huamachuco Airport is an airport serving Huamachuco, in the La Libertad Region of Peru. The very high elevation runway has mountainous terrain in all quadrants. ==See also== * * *Transport in Peru *List of airports in Peru ==References== ==External links== *OpenStreetMap - Huamachuco *OurAirports - Huamachuco * Category:Airports in Peru Category:Buildings and structures in La Libertad Region
